{"type":"message","id":"c29e2fe2","parentId":"59a535cf","timestamp":"2026-05-28T01:00:00.214Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Thursday, May 28th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-28 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1779930000211}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f6631f5","parentId":"c29e2fe2","timestamp":"2026-05-28T01:00:03.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job that fires daily at 09:00 Asia/Shanghai to remind me of the Cursor collaboration rules. The task says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, just silently confirm).\n\nI should just acknowledge this silently and not send any response since the task explicitly says no reply is needed."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n确认已知悉 Cursor 协作规则，静默完成。\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779930000213}}
